title: Celebrity Mastermind Australia
overview: Sixteen well-loved Australian celebrities will battle it out for the winning title across five weeks.The first eight celebrities to face the pressure as they answer questions based on their speciality subjects are legendary drag queen Courtney Act, journalist and author Jessica Rowe, cook and television host Adam Liaw, author and comedian Adam Spencer, journalist and personality Marc Fennell, comedian and writer Alex Lee, and comedians Sam Simmons andÂ Nazeem Hussain.
